{"tid":751218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員遭兇徒割頸成植物人","createTime":"2018-07-21T16:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T17:01:16.000Z","uid":28366,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"752d7cecd4bd6a2bbe34185d6ff7f5ee268f442b","tid":751218,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/07/20180718_CR_%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F07%2F20180718_CR_%25E6%259C%25B1%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%259C%258B-2.jpg&h=bda09fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2005年的今日，警員朱振國單獨外出巡邏，卻未料迎來無妄之災，被兇徒廖智勇利刀插向左頸，導致腦萎縮癱瘓，慘變植物人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/07/20180718_CR_%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F07%2F20180718_CR_%25E6%259C%25B1%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%259C%258B-1.jpg&h=332f9826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事發在當日早上8時半，警員朱振國當值早更，單獨外出巡邏，當巡至保安道巿政大廈對開時，發現男子廖智勇行為閃縮，遂上前截查。正當朱向電台查詢廖是否通緝犯之際，廖突然從身上拔出一把六吋長生果刀，刺向朱左邊頸部，並傷及大動脈致血流不止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/07/20180718_CR_%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F07%2F20180718_CR_%25E6%259C%25B1%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%259C%258B-4.jpg&h=7bcf9642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廖傷人後即拔足狂奔，朱則負傷尾隨追趕，並用手按着傷口，但至50米外，終告不支倒地，而兇徒在逃出10米外，轉入巿政大廈的橫巷，並棄下利刀不知所終。在當日下午1時許，廖在太子地鐵站向一名巡警自首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/07/20180718_CR_%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F07%2F20180718_CR_%25E6%259C%25B1%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%259C%258B-3.jpg&h=710a9f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廖智勇06年4月被判囚6年，期後上訴庭認為刑期過輕，改判囚10年。至於朱振國事後腦萎縮癱瘓，慘成植物人，朱事後由妻子代表入稟，向廖及警務處處長索償。案件在前年庭外和解，由政府一筆過支付賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3289156-【當年今日】05年警員朱振國巡邏-遭兇徒割脈成植\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3289156-%E3%80%90%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E3%80%9105%E5%B9%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%87%E5%BE%92%E5%89%B2%E8%84%88%E6%88%90%E6%A4%8D&d=HiwZSIYrjIamUWMmlnLe16MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=18cc9e44\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3289156-【當年今日】05年警員朱振國巡邏-遭兇徒割脈成植</a>"},{"pid":"69f4cbb81ab48163ffd6a17e4380b6363f3b53b1","tid":751218,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09b3469252581ef01b33c34b13e0ab270c46898","tid":751218,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735febc6a6ef817771e8d8d7a14f2411ca50fecb","tid":751218,"uid":189053,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"232eebc13fa78c7bce613390c6757fe82606593d","tid":751218,"uid":144567,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"735febc6a6ef817771e8d8d7a14f2411ca50fecb","tid":751218,"uid":189053,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"所以一搏命就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba53d7a9f78dec2d9fdbe2b5949dbb021f9f1bb3","tid":751218,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20